00:00:01.920 --> 00:00:03.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HEITER] It's a grimoire
written by Flamme</b></Default>

c0000001
00:00:03.830 --> 00:00:05.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the legendary mage?</b></Default>

c0000002
00:00:05.800 --> 00:00:07.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] No. Books
supposedly attributed</b></Default>

c0000003
00:00:07.720 --> 00:00:09.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to Flamme are never real.</b></Default>

c0000004
00:00:09.890 --> 00:00:12.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Every tome uncovered so far
has been a fabrication.</b></Default>

c0000005
00:00:13.930 --> 00:00:15.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is probably
the best imitation</b></Default>

c0000006
00:00:15.850 --> 00:00:17.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've come across
over the years, though.</b></Default>

c0000007
00:00:18.190 --> 00:00:20.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's not a terrible reward
to receive</b></Default>

c0000008
00:00:20.100 --> 00:00:21.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for defeating monsters.</b></Default>

c0000009
00:00:21.520 --> 00:00:23.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HIMMEL] If you say so,
I don't see the appeal.</b></Default>

c0000010
00:00:24.520 --> 00:00:25.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HEITER]
What a shame.</b></Default>

c0000011
00:00:25.610 --> 00:00:27.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When you find nothing
but forgeries,</b></Default>

c0000012
00:00:27.410 --> 00:00:29.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you start to doubt
whether the genuine article</b></Default>

c0000013
00:00:29.450 --> 00:00:31.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>ever existed
in the first place.</b></Default>

c0000014
00:00:31.570 --> 00:00:34.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EISEN] The great Flamme,
founder of humanity's magic.</b></Default>

c0000015
00:00:35.460 --> 00:00:37.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>To be fair,
it's like a fairy tale.</b></Default>

c0000016
00:00:38.120 --> 00:00:39.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Is that what people believe?</b></Default>

c0000017
00:00:41.460 --> 00:00:43.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I suppose enough years
have passed</b></Default>

c0000018
00:00:43.330 --> 00:00:45.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that she's become
something of a myth.</b></Default>

c0000019
00:00:46.880 --> 00:00:49.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I might be the only one
left alive who knew her,</b></Default>

c0000020
00:00:50.130 --> 00:00:51.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who remembers her face.</b></Default>

c0000021
00:00:54.850 --> 00:00:56.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[birds chirping]</b></Default>

c0000022
00:01:01.230 --> 00:01:02.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Good morning.</b></Default>

c0000023
00:01:03.390 --> 00:01:05.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[fire crackling]</b></Default>

c0000024
00:01:07.150 --> 00:01:09.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's a miracle!
She woke up early!</b></Default>

c0000025
00:01:09.610 --> 00:01:10.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Okay?</b></Default>

c0000026
00:01:10.570 --> 00:01:11.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And you're shocked by that?</b></Default>

c0000027
00:01:11.990 --> 00:01:12.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Astounded.</b></Default>

c0000028
00:01:14.710 --> 00:01:16.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is deserving of a reward.</b></Default>

c0000029
00:01:19.540 --> 00:01:20.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[smiles]</b></Default>

c0000030
00:01:22.160 --> 00:01:23.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[blowing]</b></Default>

c0000031
00:01:24.580 --> 00:01:26.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
What is happening?</b></Default>

c0000032
00:02:59.640 --> 00:03:00.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[thunks]</b></Default>

c0000033
00:03:02.060 --> 00:03:03.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

c0000034
00:03:04.260 --> 00:03:07.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000035
00:03:11.610 --> 00:03:13.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My most humble thanks.</b></Default>

c0000036
00:03:13.320 --> 00:03:14.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When I saw this landslide,</b></Default>

c0000037
00:03:15.080 --> 00:03:17.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I feared I would never find
a way through the pass.</b></Default>

c0000038
00:03:17.780 --> 00:03:19.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000039
00:03:24.450 --> 00:03:25.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
Hey, uh...</b></Default>

c0000040
00:03:26.290 --> 00:03:28.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is this actually necessary?</b></Default>

c0000041
00:03:28.090 --> 00:03:29.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you unhappy?</b></Default>

c0000042
00:03:29.540 --> 00:03:31.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He's offered a fine reward.</b></Default>

c0000043
00:03:31.500 --> 00:03:32.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, that's not the issue.</b></Default>

c0000044
00:03:33.090 --> 00:03:35.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This would go faster
if you just used your magic</b></Default>

c0000045
00:03:35.180 --> 00:03:36.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to move his cart.</b></Default>

c0000046
00:03:36.800 --> 00:03:38.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But what of future travelers?</b></Default>

c0000047
00:03:38.550 --> 00:03:39.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They'd be stuck here.</b></Default>

c0000048
00:03:40.050 --> 00:03:41.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's what Fern said.</b></Default>

c0000049
00:03:43.140 --> 00:03:45.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We wouldn't want to be
selfish, now would we?</b></Default>

c0000050
00:03:45.560 --> 00:03:47.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] Hah.
That's rich, coming from you.</b></Default>

c0000051
00:03:48.520 --> 00:03:49.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[fluttering]</b></Default>

c0000052
00:03:49.900 --> 00:03:51.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000053
00:03:51.480 --> 00:03:52.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I insist you have a drink.</b></Default>

c0000054
00:03:53.110 --> 00:03:54.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, thanks.
That'd be great.</b></Default>

c0000055
00:03:55.700 --> 00:03:56.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[cork plops]</b></Default>

c0000056
00:03:57.530 --> 00:03:58.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gulping]</b></Default>

c0000057
00:03:59.780 --> 00:04:00.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Stark sighs]</b></Default>

c0000058
00:04:01.780 --> 00:04:02.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's strange.</b></Default>

c0000059
00:04:03.700 --> 00:04:06.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I thought landslides happened
on a bigger scale.</b></Default>

c0000060
00:04:06.420 --> 00:04:07.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE TRAVELER 6A]
The northern lands</b></Default>

c0000061
00:04:07.460 --> 00:04:09.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>have been fighting demons
in this area,</b></Default>

c0000062
00:04:09.330 --> 00:04:11.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and their clashes have had
a far-reaching impact</b></Default>

c0000063
00:04:11.670 --> 00:04:12.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>on local terrain.</b></Default>

c0000064
00:04:12.960 --> 00:04:15.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This was likely caused
by such a skirmish.</b></Default>

c0000065
00:04:16.390 --> 00:04:18.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So now we're tending
to the scars of battle.</b></Default>

c0000066
00:04:23.300 --> 00:04:24.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
Mister Stark.</b></Default>

c0000067
00:04:25.020 --> 00:04:26.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Would you mind helping me
over here?</b></Default>

c0000068
00:04:26.900 --> 00:04:28.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I could use your assistance
for a moment.</b></Default>

c0000069
00:04:31.690 --> 00:04:32.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mister Stark?</b></Default>

c0000070
00:04:33.770 --> 00:04:34.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey.</b></Default>

c0000071
00:04:34.820 --> 00:04:36.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Could you maybe drop
the "mister" part?</b></Default>

c0000072
00:04:36.820 --> 00:04:37.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Stark is fine.</b></Default>

c0000073
00:04:39.070 --> 00:04:40.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It weirds me out.</b></Default>

c0000074
00:04:40.570 --> 00:04:42.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm pretty sure
we're close to the same age.</b></Default>

c0000075
00:04:45.000 --> 00:04:46.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Very well.</b></Default>

c0000076
00:04:46.620 --> 00:04:47.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you'd prefer it.</b></Default>

c0000077
00:04:49.500 --> 00:04:51.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Stark. You're wasting
everyone's time.</b></Default>

c0000078
00:04:51.750 --> 00:04:53.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Help me.
-Rude!</b></Default>

c0000079
00:04:53.540 --> 00:04:55.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] I just meant
that if we're gonna go</b></Default>

c0000080
00:04:55.090 --> 00:04:57.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>on this journey together,
you can drop the formalities.</b></Default>

c0000081
00:04:58.470 --> 00:05:00.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We can talk
to each other casually.</b></Default>

c0000082
00:05:00.380 --> 00:05:01.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh.</b></Default>

c0000083
00:05:01.630 --> 00:05:04.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And it wouldn't hurt you to be
a little friendlier, ya know.</b></Default>

c0000084
00:05:04.260 --> 00:05:06.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm a warrior
with a sensitive soul.</b></Default>

c0000085
00:05:06.690 --> 00:05:07.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What a pain in the rear.</b></Default>

c0000086
00:05:08.060 --> 00:05:09.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
What'd you call me?</b></Default>

c0000087
00:05:09.890 --> 00:05:11.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I assume you're making
good progress?</b></Default>

c0000088
00:05:12.480 --> 00:05:13.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
You heard her.</b></Default>

c0000089
00:05:13.520 --> 00:05:15.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's hurry, Mister Stark.</b></Default>

c0000090
00:05:16.400 --> 00:05:17.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
Fine.</b></Default>

c0000091
00:05:18.530 --> 00:05:19.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE TRAVELER 6A]
Aah!</b></Default>

c0000092
00:05:19.780 --> 00:05:21.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You have my undying gratitude.</b></Default>

c0000093
00:05:21.990 --> 00:05:25.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you'd like, I can show you
the fastest route into town.</b></Default>

c0000094
00:05:26.080 --> 00:05:28.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have the honor
of escorting an elf, eh?</b></Default>

c0000095
00:05:29.080 --> 00:05:30.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've lived for many decades,</b></Default>

c0000096
00:05:30.620 --> 00:05:33.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but this is my first time
meeting one of your kind.</b></Default>

c0000097
00:05:33.660 --> 00:05:35.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I suppose we are a rarity.</b></Default>

c0000098
00:05:36.130 --> 00:05:38.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] Huh. Now that
I'm thinking about it,</b></Default>

c0000099
00:05:38.510 --> 00:05:40.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you're the only one
I've ever seen in person, too.</b></Default>

c0000100
00:05:41.130 --> 00:05:42.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
There aren't very many of us.</b></Default>

c0000101
00:05:44.050 --> 00:05:45.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In fact, I've only ever met</b></Default>

c0000102
00:05:45.390 --> 00:05:47.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a handful of other elves
in all my travels.</b></Default>

c0000103
00:05:48.430 --> 00:05:49.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We may live a long time,</b></Default>

c0000104
00:05:49.930 --> 00:05:51.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but we've scattered
to the winds.</b></Default>

c0000105
00:05:52.100 --> 00:05:55.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Of course, it doesn't help that
we don't have romantic urges</b></Default>

c0000106
00:05:55.110 --> 00:05:56.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>or reproductive instincts.</b></Default>

c0000107
00:05:57.570 --> 00:05:59.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're experiencing
a quiet extinction.</b></Default>

c0000108
00:06:00.360 --> 00:06:02.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Over 400 years have gone by</b></Default>

c0000109
00:06:02.360 --> 00:06:04.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>since I've laid eyes
on another elf.</b></Default>

c0000110
00:06:05.000 --> 00:06:06.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We may be close
to disappearing.</b></Default>

c0000111
00:06:06.950 --> 00:06:08.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000112
00:06:08.750 --> 00:06:11.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[wheels rattling]</b></Default>

c0000113
00:06:16.300 --> 00:06:18.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is a lovely view
of the town.</b></Default>

c0000114
00:06:19.510 --> 00:06:21.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's a busy day at the gate.</b></Default>

c0000115
00:06:21.960 --> 00:06:23.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Those look like
merchant wagons.</b></Default>

c0000116
00:06:23.550 --> 00:06:25.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The Liberation Festival
is tonight.</b></Default>

c0000117
00:06:27.270 --> 00:06:29.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was on this very day
many moons ago</b></Default>

c0000118
00:06:30.470 --> 00:06:32.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that Himmel
and his party of heroes</b></Default>

c0000119
00:06:32.350 --> 00:06:35.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>defeated the demons
who plagued this land.</b></Default>

c0000120
00:06:36.280 --> 00:06:38.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That must have been
quite the experience for them.</b></Default>

c0000121
00:06:39.730 --> 00:06:41.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE TRAVELER 6A]
The Liberation Festival</b></Default>

c0000122
00:06:41.190 --> 00:06:43.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>commemorates their triumph.</b></Default>

c0000123
00:06:43.650 --> 00:06:45.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Every year, the statues
of Mister Himmel</b></Default>

c0000124
00:06:45.620 --> 00:06:47.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and his companions
in the central plaza</b></Default>

c0000125
00:06:47.660 --> 00:06:49.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>are decorated,
and the town throws</b></Default>

c0000126
00:06:49.540 --> 00:06:51.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a grand celebration
around them.</b></Default>

c0000127
00:06:52.450 --> 00:06:54.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Humans love to make a fuss.</b></Default>

c0000128
00:06:54.700 --> 00:06:56.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They'll use any excuse
to hold a festival.</b></Default>

c0000129
00:06:57.300 --> 00:06:58.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>More than 80 years have passed</b></Default>

c0000130
00:06:58.920 --> 00:07:00.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>since the demons
were finally defeated</b></Default>

c0000131
00:07:00.750 --> 00:07:02.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>on that auspicious day.</b></Default>

c0000132
00:07:03.210 --> 00:07:06.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's plenty of time
for even something so important</b></Default>

c0000133
00:07:06.100 --> 00:07:08.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to begin fading
from the minds of men.</b></Default>

c0000134
00:07:09.390 --> 00:07:11.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But we can't have that.</b></Default>

c0000135
00:07:12.390 --> 00:07:13.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And so we celebrate</b></Default>

c0000136
00:07:14.350 --> 00:07:17.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in remembrance of those
who fought on our behalf.</b></Default>

c0000137
00:07:17.190 --> 00:07:19.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[wheels rattling]</b></Default>

c0000138
00:07:19.900 --> 00:07:20.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HIMMEL]
Hm.</b></Default>

c0000139
00:07:21.770 --> 00:07:22.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Excellent work.</b></Default>

c0000140
00:07:24.440 --> 00:07:26.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HEITER]
The fifth time's a charm.</b></Default>

c0000141
00:07:26.410 --> 00:07:28.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This sculptor worked faster
than previous ones.</b></Default>

c0000142
00:07:29.410 --> 00:07:31.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You are constantly
getting statues</b></Default>

c0000143
00:07:31.450 --> 00:07:32.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>put up in your honor, Himmel.</b></Default>

c0000144
00:07:33.530 --> 00:07:36.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, how else can I assure
that people will remember us?</b></Default>

c0000145
00:07:37.460 --> 00:07:39.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Our lives are fleeting
compared to yours.</b></Default>

c0000146
00:07:39.880 --> 00:07:41.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We won't be around for long.</b></Default>

c0000147
00:07:42.670 --> 00:07:44.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Take a look at this face.</b></Default>

c0000148
00:07:44.250 --> 00:07:46.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Future generations must see
how handsome I was.</b></Default>

c0000149
00:07:46.680 --> 00:07:48.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Whatever.
I'm heading back to the inn.</b></Default>

c0000150
00:07:49.890 --> 00:07:52.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Though...there is
a greater reason.</b></Default>

c0000151
00:07:53.800 --> 00:07:55.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When we three are gone,</b></Default>

c0000152
00:07:55.560 --> 00:07:58.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>maybe our statues will keep you
from feeling lonely.</b></Default>

c0000153
00:08:00.270 --> 00:08:01.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Come again?</b></Default>

c0000154
00:08:02.610 --> 00:08:03.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You'll know we existed.</b></Default>

c0000155
00:08:04.730 --> 00:08:06.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That we aren't just
fairy tales,</b></Default>

c0000156
00:08:06.660 --> 00:08:08.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but people who stood
beside you.</b></Default>

c0000157
00:08:08.820 --> 00:08:12.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

c0000158
00:08:13.570 --> 00:08:15.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Every year,
we gather in celebration</b></Default>

c0000159
00:08:15.790 --> 00:08:16.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of the spectacular deeds</b></Default>

c0000160
00:08:17.040 --> 00:08:19.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>accomplished by this
brave band of heroes.</b></Default>

c0000161
00:08:21.380 --> 00:08:22.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now that we're here,</b></Default>

c0000162
00:08:22.670 --> 00:08:25.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I must say that you bear
a striking resemblance</b></Default>

c0000163
00:08:25.140 --> 00:08:27.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to Miss Frieren,
that mighty mage of yore.</b></Default>

c0000164
00:08:30.220 --> 00:08:31.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Will they still be doing this</b></Default>

c0000165
00:08:31.640 --> 00:08:32.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>100 years from now?</b></Default>

c0000166
00:08:33.220 --> 00:08:34.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, yes.</b></Default>

c0000167
00:08:34.390 --> 00:08:36.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For as long
as this town stands.</b></Default>

c0000168
00:08:36.900 --> 00:08:37.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A 1,000 years?</b></Default>

c0000169
00:08:38.440 --> 00:08:39.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE TRAVELER 6A]
Hmm.</b></Default>

c0000170
00:08:39.810 --> 00:08:42.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's more difficult
to foresee.</b></Default>

c0000171
00:08:45.530 --> 00:08:48.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[birds chirping]</b></Default>

c0000172
00:08:48.910 --> 00:08:50.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Well? Shall we be off?</b></Default>

c0000173
00:08:51.610 --> 00:08:53.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We have a long road
ahead of us.</b></Default>

c0000174
00:08:54.570 --> 00:08:55.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
Speaking of which,</b></Default>

c0000175
00:08:56.420 --> 00:08:58.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you haven't told me what
our final destination is yet.</b></Default>

c0000176
00:08:59.580 --> 00:09:00.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Where're we going?</b></Default>

c0000177
00:09:00.960 --> 00:09:03.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000178
00:09:03.540 --> 00:09:04.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
To Heaven.</b></Default>

c0000179
00:09:05.220 --> 00:09:07.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
Huh. That sounds fun.</b></Default>

c0000180
00:09:08.510 --> 00:09:10.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000181
00:09:19.350 --> 00:09:22.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

c0000182
00:09:24.940 --> 00:09:26.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There are a lot of guards here.</b></Default>

c0000183
00:09:27.360 --> 00:09:28.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you suppose
something happened?</b></Default>

c0000184
00:09:30.110 --> 00:09:31.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Maybe we should decide
who'll be in charge</b></Default>

c0000185
00:09:31.780 --> 00:09:32.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of the shopping.</b></Default>

c0000186
00:09:36.830 --> 00:09:37.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[thuds]</b></Default>

c0000187
00:09:37.870 --> 00:09:38.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000188
00:09:40.540 --> 00:09:42.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're in town,
Mistress Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000189
00:09:42.960 --> 00:09:44.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Demons approach.
-Huh?</b></Default>

c0000190
00:09:45.130 --> 00:09:47.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000191
00:09:52.670 --> 00:09:54.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000192
00:09:55.930 --> 00:09:58.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Fiend! -[gasps]
-You'd doom us all?</b></Default>

c0000193
00:09:58.980 --> 00:10:00.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000194
00:10:05.610 --> 00:10:06.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, Graf Granat.</b></Default>

c0000195
00:10:07.690 --> 00:10:09.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did you hire an elf to kill us?</b></Default>

c0000196
00:10:10.320 --> 00:10:11.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't take credit.</b></Default>

c0000197
00:10:12.240 --> 00:10:13.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Though it's true I despise you</b></Default>

c0000198
00:10:13.820 --> 00:10:15.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and pray for your death,
Lord Lugner...</b></Default>

c0000199
00:10:16.370 --> 00:10:18.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wouldn't be so bold
as to openly attack</b></Default>

c0000200
00:10:18.450 --> 00:10:20.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a peace envoy
in the center of town.</b></Default>

c0000201
00:10:20.950 --> 00:10:21.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm no fool.</b></Default>

c0000202
00:10:22.500 --> 00:10:23.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's a peace envoy?</b></Default>

c0000203
00:10:25.000 --> 00:10:26.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GRANAT]
They're probably adventurers</b></Default>

c0000204
00:10:26.710 --> 00:10:28.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who don't understand
what's going on here.</b></Default>

c0000205
00:10:29.840 --> 00:10:31.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Certainly,
if that's your story.</b></Default>

c0000206
00:10:34.840 --> 00:10:37.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But in these cold,
calculating eyes,</b></Default>

c0000207
00:10:38.020 --> 00:10:39.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I see bloodlust.</b></Default>

c0000208
00:10:40.770 --> 00:10:42.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I know how the townsfolk feel.</b></Default>

c0000209
00:10:42.720 --> 00:10:44.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They tremble
at the sight of me.</b></Default>

c0000210
00:10:44.850 --> 00:10:46.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Loathe my existence.</b></Default>

c0000211
00:10:46.570 --> 00:10:49.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But despite that,
they still view me as a person.</b></Default>

c0000212
00:10:50.440 --> 00:10:51.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not you.</b></Default>

c0000213
00:10:51.690 --> 00:10:53.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Whenever you look at my face,</b></Default>

c0000214
00:10:53.650 --> 00:10:56.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you see only a wild beast
that should be put down.</b></Default>

c0000215
00:10:56.830 --> 00:10:58.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And is that not what you are?</b></Default>

c0000216
00:10:58.910 --> 00:11:01.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Demons are simply monsters
who have learned human speech.</b></Default>

c0000217
00:11:02.740 --> 00:11:04.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You only communicate with lies.</b></Default>

c0000218
00:11:06.710 --> 00:11:08.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GRANAT] Throw her
in the mansion's dungeon.</b></Default>

c0000219
00:11:08.960 --> 00:11:09.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE GUARD 7A]
My lord.</b></Default>

c0000220
00:11:10.050 --> 00:11:11.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000221
00:11:11.170 --> 00:11:12.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000222
00:11:16.220 --> 00:11:18.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh... Hey! Wait!</b></Default>

c0000223
00:11:18.560 --> 00:11:19.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh...</b></Default>

c0000224
00:11:20.140 --> 00:11:21.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

c0000225
00:11:32.610 --> 00:11:34.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is so boring.</b></Default>

c0000226
00:11:35.700 --> 00:11:36.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm?</b></Default>

c0000227
00:11:38.660 --> 00:11:40.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We have bad news.</b></Default>

c0000228
00:11:40.870 --> 00:11:43.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They say you'll be down here
for two or three years.</b></Default>

c0000229
00:11:43.620 --> 00:11:45.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
A shorter term than I expected.</b></Default>

c0000230
00:11:46.420 --> 00:11:48.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Could you bring me
a few grimoires later?</b></Default>

c0000231
00:11:49.670 --> 00:11:52.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I know you don't experience
time as humans do,</b></Default>

c0000232
00:11:52.250 --> 00:11:53.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but this is going
a bit too far.</b></Default>

c0000233
00:11:54.170 --> 00:11:56.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's not as though
I actively chose</b></Default>

c0000234
00:11:56.100 --> 00:11:57.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to be locked away.</b></Default>

c0000235
00:11:58.180 --> 00:11:59.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, what did he mean</b></Default>

c0000236
00:11:59.760 --> 00:12:02.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when he called those demons
peace envoys?</b></Default>

c0000237
00:12:02.720 --> 00:12:04.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I tried to get some information
while shopping.</b></Default>

c0000238
00:12:05.650 --> 00:12:06.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Aura the Guillotine.</b></Default>

c0000239
00:12:07.020 --> 00:12:08.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You have heard of her, right?</b></Default>

c0000240
00:12:08.650 --> 00:12:10.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The Seven Sages of Destruction.</b></Default>

c0000241
00:12:11.060 --> 00:12:12.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And Aura was one of them.</b></Default>

c0000242
00:12:13.730 --> 00:12:15.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She was a servant
of the Demon King.</b></Default>

c0000243
00:12:15.700 --> 00:12:17.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We killed
most of her followers,</b></Default>

c0000244
00:12:17.240 --> 00:12:19.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but she slipped away
and disappeared.</b></Default>

c0000245
00:12:19.870 --> 00:12:20.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Has she re-emerged?</b></Default>

c0000246
00:12:21.740 --> 00:12:22.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Afraid so.</b></Default>

c0000247
00:12:22.910 --> 00:12:25.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm told that she came back
to power 28 years ago.</b></Default>

c0000248
00:12:26.540 --> 00:12:28.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Since then, her forces
have been locked</b></Default>

c0000249
00:12:28.330 --> 00:12:29.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in battle with this town.</b></Default>

c0000250
00:12:29.750 --> 00:12:31.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There have been
many casualties.</b></Default>

c0000251
00:12:32.040 --> 00:12:33.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But the demons
have grown exhausted</b></Default>

c0000252
00:12:33.630 --> 00:12:34.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>by the endless fighting.</b></Default>

c0000253
00:12:35.340 --> 00:12:37.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They've come here
to propose a truce.</b></Default>

c0000254
00:12:37.930 --> 00:12:40.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Which is why
they were let inside as envoys.</b></Default>

c0000255
00:12:41.010 --> 00:12:42.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How unwise.</b></Default>

c0000256
00:12:42.680 --> 00:12:45.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's no use trying
to negotiate with their kind.</b></Default>

c0000257
00:12:46.400 --> 00:12:48.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Surely some good
can come of it.</b></Default>

c0000258
00:12:48.400 --> 00:12:49.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why not speak to them?</b></Default>

c0000259
00:12:49.900 --> 00:12:51.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wouldn't the best option
be to stop fighting</b></Default>

c0000260
00:12:51.690 --> 00:12:53.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and start talking
their problems out?</b></Default>

c0000261
00:12:53.730 --> 00:12:56.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No. Nothing will be
resolved that way.</b></Default>

c0000262
00:12:58.280 --> 00:13:00.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Demons are beasts
who seek to devour.</b></Default>

c0000263
00:13:01.110 --> 00:13:03.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Have you ever wondered
why those monsters</b></Default>

c0000264
00:13:03.160 --> 00:13:05.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>chose to speak
the same language as humans?</b></Default>

c0000265
00:13:07.170 --> 00:13:10.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000266
00:13:10.460 --> 00:13:11.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE VILLAGER 7C]
Please, Hero.</b></Default>

c0000267
00:13:11.620 --> 00:13:13.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You must slay this devil!</b></Default>

c0000268
00:13:15.720 --> 00:13:17.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[shuddered breathing]</b></Default>

c0000269
00:13:18.180 --> 00:13:19.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HIMMEL]
It's only a child.</b></Default>

c0000270
00:13:19.970 --> 00:13:22.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No. Don't be fooled
by its appearance.</b></Default>

c0000271
00:13:22.380 --> 00:13:23.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It ate her.</b></Default>

c0000272
00:13:23.340 --> 00:13:25.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My daughter is dead.
Swing your sword!</b></Default>

c0000273
00:13:26.730 --> 00:13:29.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[footsteps approaching]</b></Default>

c0000274
00:13:31.640 --> 00:13:32.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-It hurts.
-[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000275
00:13:33.270 --> 00:13:35.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000276
00:13:35.450 --> 00:13:36.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Make it stop.</b></Default>

c0000277
00:13:38.110 --> 00:13:39.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please, Mommy.</b></Default>

c0000278
00:13:40.860 --> 00:13:41.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[shuddered breathing]</b></Default>

c0000279
00:13:46.250 --> 00:13:47.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Step away.</b></Default>

c0000280
00:13:47.500 --> 00:13:48.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll handle this.</b></Default>

c0000281
00:13:49.410 --> 00:13:50.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE VILLAGER 6C]
Kill her...</b></Default>

c0000282
00:13:50.830 --> 00:13:52.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and we'd be no better
than them.</b></Default>

c0000283
00:13:54.830 --> 00:13:57.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My friends,
surely this scared little girl</b></Default>

c0000284
00:13:57.130 --> 00:13:59.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>can eat what we do
in order to survive.</b></Default>

c0000285
00:14:00.050 --> 00:14:01.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why don't we give her
the opportunity</b></Default>

c0000286
00:14:01.880 --> 00:14:03.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-to atone for her mistakes?
-[crying]</b></Default>

c0000287
00:14:03.920 --> 00:14:05.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, chief, you can't.</b></Default>

c0000288
00:14:05.220 --> 00:14:06.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you crazy?</b></Default>

c0000289
00:14:07.020 --> 00:14:08.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It took our daughter!</b></Default>

c0000290
00:14:08.850 --> 00:14:10.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll never hold her again.</b></Default>

c0000291
00:14:11.140 --> 00:14:14.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crying]</b></Default>

c0000292
00:14:15.900 --> 00:14:17.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE VILLAGER 6C] Here.
Let me tend to your wounds.</b></Default>

c0000293
00:14:18.820 --> 00:14:19.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're in luck.</b></Default>

c0000294
00:14:20.070 --> 00:14:22.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've been looking for somebody
to help out around the farm.</b></Default>

c0000295
00:14:25.110 --> 00:14:26.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Himmel.</b></Default>

c0000296
00:14:26.330 --> 00:14:28.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're going to regret
not killing this girl.</b></Default>

c0000297
00:14:28.950 --> 00:14:29.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This demon.</b></Default>

c0000298
00:14:30.450 --> 00:14:31.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's here.</b></Default>

c0000299
00:14:31.830 --> 00:14:33.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why don't you speak
to her and see?</b></Default>

c0000300
00:14:34.580 --> 00:14:36.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We'll be in this village
for some time, anyway.</b></Default>

c0000301
00:14:37.010 --> 00:14:38.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We might as well try.</b></Default>

c0000302
00:14:41.420 --> 00:14:42.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Fine.</b></Default>

c0000303
00:14:44.510 --> 00:14:46.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000304
00:15:09.700 --> 00:15:12.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[fire roaring]</b></Default>

c0000305
00:15:16.380 --> 00:15:18.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why did you murder
the village chief?</b></Default>

c0000306
00:15:18.550 --> 00:15:21.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[fire roaring]</b></Default>

c0000307
00:15:24.210 --> 00:15:25.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We should've killed it at once.</b></Default>

c0000308
00:15:26.100 --> 00:15:28.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>These monsters
cannot live among us.</b></Default>

c0000309
00:15:28.970 --> 00:15:30.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There it is again.</b></Default>

c0000310
00:15:33.140 --> 00:15:35.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Every day since I came here,</b></Default>

c0000311
00:15:35.140 --> 00:15:36.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've felt your desire
to kill me.</b></Default>

c0000312
00:15:37.860 --> 00:15:39.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I just wanted
to live in harmony.</b></Default>

c0000313
00:15:40.940 --> 00:15:43.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I figured out a way
to make things right.</b></Default>

c0000314
00:15:43.770 --> 00:15:45.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Here, take this child
as a replacement</b></Default>

c0000315
00:15:46.330 --> 00:15:47.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-for your offspring...
-[all gasp]</b></Default>

c0000316
00:15:48.080 --> 00:15:49.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>...the one I ate.</b></Default>

c0000317
00:15:50.490 --> 00:15:52.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That girl is the daughter
of the village chief.</b></Default>

c0000318
00:15:53.620 --> 00:15:55.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, but he isn't alive
anymore.</b></Default>

c0000319
00:15:58.920 --> 00:15:59.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[swords clanging]</b></Default>

c0000320
00:16:02.500 --> 00:16:04.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Despite my good intentions,</b></Default>

c0000321
00:16:04.500 --> 00:16:06.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it seems as though
I have unfortunately made</b></Default>

c0000322
00:16:06.470 --> 00:16:07.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>another mistake.</b></Default>

c0000323
00:16:07.680 --> 00:16:09.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You've given me no choice.</b></Default>

c0000324
00:16:09.600 --> 00:16:11.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-I'm taking this child hostage.
-[sword clanging]</b></Default>

c0000325
00:16:15.220 --> 00:16:18.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000326
00:16:18.690 --> 00:16:20.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You won't stop me again?</b></Default>

c0000327
00:16:21.400 --> 00:16:22.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No.</b></Default>

c0000328
00:16:23.310 --> 00:16:24.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mommy, please.</b></Default>

c0000329
00:16:24.730 --> 00:16:25.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[thuds]</b></Default>

c0000330
00:16:25.820 --> 00:16:28.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000331
00:16:31.280 --> 00:16:32.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why call out to a mother?</b></Default>

c0000332
00:16:33.870 --> 00:16:36.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Demons are monsters,
and like all monsters,</b></Default>

c0000333
00:16:36.420 --> 00:16:37.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>they don't raise their young.</b></Default>

c0000334
00:16:38.130 --> 00:16:40.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Once born, you are abandoned.</b></Default>

c0000335
00:16:40.330 --> 00:16:42.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You walk this world alone.</b></Default>

c0000336
00:16:43.250 --> 00:16:46.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That makes you ruthless,
solitary creatures.</b></Default>

c0000337
00:16:46.390 --> 00:16:49.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Lone wolves with no concept
of what family means.</b></Default>

c0000338
00:16:50.550 --> 00:16:51.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Explain.</b></Default>

c0000339
00:16:51.890 --> 00:16:53.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why would you call out
to a mother</b></Default>

c0000340
00:16:53.510 --> 00:16:54.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you've never known?</b></Default>

c0000341
00:16:56.270 --> 00:16:57.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's simple.</b></Default>

c0000342
00:16:58.100 --> 00:16:59.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That word stops humans.</b></Default>

c0000343
00:17:00.900 --> 00:17:02.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It keeps them
from murdering us.</b></Default>

c0000344
00:17:03.100 --> 00:17:04.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Isn't that magical?</b></Default>

c0000345
00:17:08.160 --> 00:17:10.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Demons use words
to trick humans.</b></Default>

c0000346
00:17:10.530 --> 00:17:12.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can't trust
a thing they say.</b></Default>

c0000347
00:17:13.360 --> 00:17:15.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They're monsters
who learned to speak.</b></Default>

c0000348
00:17:15.450 --> 00:17:18.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's how the legendary mage
Flamme defined them.</b></Default>

c0000349
00:17:18.960 --> 00:17:20.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's in their blood.</b></Default>

c0000350
00:17:20.330 --> 00:17:22.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They're descended from liars.</b></Default>

c0000351
00:17:22.830 --> 00:17:24.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Monsters who found
they could lure in humans</b></Default>

c0000352
00:17:24.960 --> 00:17:26.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>by crying, "Help me."</b></Default>

c0000353
00:17:28.090 --> 00:17:31.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[footsteps]</b></Default>

c0000354
00:17:31.970 --> 00:17:33.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Don't forget
about the grimoires.</b></Default>

c0000355
00:17:39.190 --> 00:17:40.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DRAHT]
Granat is late.</b></Default>

c0000356
00:17:40.730 --> 00:17:41.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[scoffs]
What insolence.</b></Default>

c0000357
00:17:42.350 --> 00:17:44.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's a human diplomatic tactic.</b></Default>

c0000358
00:17:45.610 --> 00:17:49.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Frankly, I'm more curious
about the rouge mage.</b></Default>

c0000359
00:17:50.360 --> 00:17:52.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've seen her face before.</b></Default>

c0000360
00:17:54.860 --> 00:17:57.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wild beasts
who only communicate with lies.</b></Default>

c0000361
00:17:58.540 --> 00:18:00.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's not
an inaccurate description.</b></Default>

c0000362
00:18:01.500 --> 00:18:03.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She can see us for what we are.</b></Default>

c0000363
00:18:03.540 --> 00:18:06.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No one else in this town
understands our true nature.</b></Default>

c0000364
00:18:07.420 --> 00:18:09.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Or perhaps, she's just logical.</b></Default>

c0000365
00:18:09.470 --> 00:18:11.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She knows
there's but one reason</b></Default>

c0000366
00:18:11.260 --> 00:18:12.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to learn our prey's language.</b></Default>

c0000367
00:18:13.840 --> 00:18:16.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They talk to us
so that they may deceive us.</b></Default>

c0000368
00:18:16.640 --> 00:18:18.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Every word is a baited trap.</b></Default>

c0000369
00:18:19.730 --> 00:18:21.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This town won't be standing
for much longer.</b></Default>

c0000370
00:18:22.730 --> 00:18:25.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I should use the confusion
as a cover to escape.</b></Default>

c0000371
00:18:26.110 --> 00:18:27.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[doors thudding]</b></Default>

c0000372
00:18:27.570 --> 00:18:30.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[footsteps]</b></Default>

c0000373
00:18:33.240 --> 00:18:34.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Where are we?</b></Default>

c0000374
00:18:35.870 --> 00:18:37.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is my son's room.</b></Default>

c0000375
00:18:41.540 --> 00:18:42.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He was a good boy.</b></Default>

c0000376
00:18:43.910 --> 00:18:46.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He'd often boast that he'd take
control of the family soon,</b></Default>

c0000377
00:18:47.340 --> 00:18:49.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>offering me a chance
to finally relax.</b></Default>

c0000378
00:18:49.710 --> 00:18:52.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[footsteps]</b></Default>

c0000379
00:18:57.180 --> 00:18:59.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He fought bravely
alongside His Majesty,</b></Default>

c0000380
00:18:59.560 --> 00:19:01.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who then gifted him this sword.</b></Default>

c0000381
00:19:01.680 --> 00:19:03.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And where might
your son be now?</b></Default>

c0000382
00:19:04.520 --> 00:19:05.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sword clanging]</b></Default>

c0000383
00:19:07.900 --> 00:19:10.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He died in battle
against your leader, Aura,</b></Default>

c0000384
00:19:10.320 --> 00:19:11.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>ten years ago.</b></Default>

c0000385
00:19:14.650 --> 00:19:17.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[heavy footsteps]</b></Default>

c0000386
00:19:19.370 --> 00:19:21.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GRANAT] This sword is all
that was left of him.</b></Default>

c0000387
00:19:22.330 --> 00:19:23.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You monster!</b></Default>

c0000388
00:19:26.210 --> 00:19:28.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I invited you here
to avenge my boy,</b></Default>

c0000389
00:19:28.840 --> 00:19:30.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the child you took from me.</b></Default>

c0000390
00:19:30.880 --> 00:19:32.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I will slaughter you
in his name.</b></Default>

c0000391
00:19:33.460 --> 00:19:35.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your peace means nothing to me!</b></Default>

c0000392
00:19:37.220 --> 00:19:39.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000393
00:19:46.650 --> 00:19:48.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Allow me to compliment
the tidiness</b></Default>

c0000394
00:19:48.770 --> 00:19:49.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of your son's room.</b></Default>

c0000395
00:19:50.860 --> 00:19:53.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wager you've kept it
just as it was ten years ago.</b></Default>

c0000396
00:19:54.940 --> 00:19:56.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What does it matter to you?</b></Default>

c0000397
00:19:57.080 --> 00:19:58.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've kept my father's room
the same</b></Default>

c0000398
00:19:58.990 --> 00:20:00.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>since he was lost to us, too.</b></Default>

c0000399
00:20:00.830 --> 00:20:02.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>From when you struck him down.</b></Default>

c0000400
00:20:02.950 --> 00:20:03.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000401
00:20:04.870 --> 00:20:06.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We can put an end
to all of this.</b></Default>

c0000402
00:20:06.790 --> 00:20:07.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't you see?</b></Default>

c0000403
00:20:08.710 --> 00:20:11.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Or we can go on spilling
each other's blood,</b></Default>

c0000404
00:20:11.840 --> 00:20:14.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>causing more grief,
ruining more lives.</b></Default>

c0000405
00:20:17.390 --> 00:20:18.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We can speak
to one another,</b></Default>

c0000406
00:20:18.760 --> 00:20:19.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>can we not?</b></Default>

c0000407
00:20:19.890 --> 00:20:22.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So please.
Let's find another way.</b></Default>

c0000408
00:20:23.470 --> 00:20:24.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[clanking]</b></Default>

c0000409
00:20:25.550 --> 00:20:26.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[shuddered breathing]</b></Default>

c0000410
00:20:26.940 --> 00:20:29.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000411
00:20:31.400 --> 00:20:33.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[swords clanking]</b></Default>

c0000412
00:20:33.940 --> 00:20:35.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GRANAT]
Show them to the guestroom.</b></Default>

c0000413
00:20:35.610 --> 00:20:37.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000414
00:20:41.990 --> 00:20:43.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I shall consider this.</b></Default>

c0000415
00:20:44.280 --> 00:20:47.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[footsteps receding]</b></Default>

c0000416
00:20:50.880 --> 00:20:52.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[footsteps approaching]</b></Default>

c0000417
00:20:52.880 --> 00:20:53.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Lord Lugner.</b></Default>

c0000418
00:20:54.380 --> 00:20:55.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-What is a father?
-[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000419
00:20:57.220 --> 00:20:58.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Who can say?</b></Default>

c0000420
00:21:00.010 --> 00:21:02.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gurgling]</b></Default>

c0000421
00:21:07.520 --> 00:21:09.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Graf Granat resents us,</b></Default>

c0000422
00:21:09.350 --> 00:21:11.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but he is also
an empathetic man.</b></Default>

c0000423
00:21:11.480 --> 00:21:13.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And that's a flaw
we can wield against him.</b></Default>

c0000424
00:21:15.400 --> 00:21:16.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I aim to win his trust.</b></Default>

c0000425
00:21:16.910 --> 00:21:17.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And if I do,</b></Default>

c0000426
00:21:17.950 --> 00:21:20.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll ask him to lower
the town's defensive barrier</b></Default>

c0000427
00:21:20.410 --> 00:21:21.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>as a show of good faith.</b></Default>

c0000428
00:21:22.570 --> 00:21:24.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then Lady Aura's forces
will raze</b></Default>

c0000429
00:21:24.700 --> 00:21:26.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>this meddlesome town and feast.</b></Default>

c0000430
00:21:27.120 --> 00:21:29.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000431
00:21:30.460 --> 00:21:31.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[chomps]
-I can't help but notice</b></Default>

c0000432
00:21:32.000 --> 00:21:33.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it's just you and me, Linie.</b></Default>

c0000433
00:21:34.080 --> 00:21:35.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Where has Draht run off to?</b></Default>

c0000434
00:21:35.880 --> 00:21:38.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He said he was eliminating
an obstacle.</b></Default>

c0000435
00:21:39.260 --> 00:21:40.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How irresponsible.</b></Default>

c0000436
00:21:41.470 --> 00:21:43.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What will I do
with that reckless youth?</b></Default>

c0000437
00:21:45.300 --> 00:21:47.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[footsteps approaching]</b></Default>

c0000438
00:21:47.850 --> 00:21:48.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Lord Draht!</b></Default>

c0000439
00:21:49.100 --> 00:21:50.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This area is forbidden
to guests.</b></Default>

c0000440
00:21:51.020 --> 00:21:52.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why are you here?</b></Default>

c0000441
00:21:52.600 --> 00:21:54.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Please return to...
-[tinkling]</b></Default>

c0000442
00:21:55.640 --> 00:21:56.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[thudding]</b></Default>

c0000443
00:22:01.950 --> 00:22:03.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[cell door opening]</b></Default>

c0000444
00:22:05.780 --> 00:22:06.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sorry.</b></Default>

c0000445
00:22:06.870 --> 00:22:08.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm told
visiting hours are over.</b></Default>

c0000446
00:22:11.500 --> 00:22:13.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm an executioner.
Name's Draht.</b></Default>

c0000447
00:22:13.870 --> 00:22:15.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I serve Aura the Guillotine.</b></Default>

c0000448
00:22:15.620 --> 00:22:16.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't fight.</b></Default>

c0000449
00:22:17.050 --> 00:22:18.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have come here to kill you.</b></Default>

c0000450
00:22:19.920 --> 00:22:20.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I see.</b></Default>

c0000451
00:22:21.220 --> 00:22:23.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not pretending
you want peace anymore?</b></Default>

c0000452
00:22:24.090 --> 00:22:25.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We've just begun.</b></Default>

c0000453
00:22:26.140 --> 00:22:27.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

c0000454
00:22:27.520 --> 00:22:28.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DRAHT]
According to Lord Lugner,</b></Default>

c0000455
00:22:29.390 --> 00:22:32.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>this girl is the only obstacle
standing in our way.</b></Default>

c0000456
00:22:32.770 --> 00:22:34.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I dispose of her now,</b></Default>

c0000457
00:22:34.600 --> 00:22:36.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and we get Graf Granat
to trust us,</b></Default>

c0000458
00:22:37.490 --> 00:22:38.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>this town will crumble.</b></Default>

c0000459
00:22:40.440 --> 00:22:42.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I should warn you
that I am fairly strong.</b></Default>

c0000460
00:22:44.530 --> 00:22:45.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Stronger than me?</b></Default>

c0000461
00:22:46.870 --> 00:22:49.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Stronger even
than Aura the Guillotine.</b></Default>

c0000462
00:24:20.210 --> 00:24:21.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [LINIE] Who is that mage,
exactly? -[GRANAT] It's a</b></Default>

c0000463
00:24:21.670 --> 00:24:23.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>serious crime
to speak to me in such a tone.</b></Default>

c0000464
00:24:23.250 --> 00:24:25.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] You'd be sentenced
to death for killing the guard.</b></Default>

c0000465
00:24:25.170 --> 00:24:27.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LUGNER] That bloodthirsty mage
sent more demons</b></Default>

c0000466
00:24:27.850 --> 00:24:29.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to the grave
than anyone else in history.</b></Default>

